Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.56,0:00:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.47,0:00:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You are... different than Akura-ou!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a fox than understands people's pain, aren't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.90,0:00:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...say that you don't hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just what {\i0}am{\i1} I saying!?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.72,0:00:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't... hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.09,0:00:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the cruel Tomoe's heart had changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Tomoe of 500 years ago is much more rough than he is today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.12,0:00:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My body too seems to move better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.69,0:00:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He calls me Yukiji.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.21,0:01:01.10,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(280,270}The God\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\NGoes to Meet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.45,0:01:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want it. I've lost appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.65,0:01:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I'm not Yukiji.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.78,0:01:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared... of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I just said I don't hate you. I won't go together with you though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.08,0:01:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be returning home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.74,0:01:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,To your fiancé's place, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.10,0:01:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You were about to get married, but human men are all worms.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.32,0:01:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Even then, do you still want to become such a man's bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.37,0:01:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.65,0:01:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they are insignificant for you, they are my precious in-laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... is this also something you received from that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.49,0:01:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw this lying in the hut from just now and picked it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.15,0:01:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you receive this from that worm man?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:01:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's mine, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.98,0:02:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...received this hairpin from Tomoe, that's why.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my favourite. Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.59,0:02:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All you do is get angry or cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.84,0:02:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Come. I'll show you something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.36,0:02:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't go! I won't go together with you, Tomoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that? You don't hate me, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the problem here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.12,0:02:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then are you scared of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In fact, I really like you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.81,0:02:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really like you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, right now... the person reflected in Tomoe's eyes... isn't me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not-{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Cherry blossoms!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the same flowers as your hairpin, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you pleased?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.34,0:03:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like being inside a dream, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.11,0:03:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My legs are still unsteady.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,0:03:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Always be that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Smile.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forgive me, Tomoe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The one hearing those words... shouldn't even be me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're this pleased with this place, I shall build a palace here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, you can view the cherry blossoms whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But Tomoe, the cherry blossoms will scatter eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I, too, must return home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's okay, won't you drop me at my home? Just saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.48,0:04:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like this way of talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember? That rainy day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:05:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...I met you for the first time in that miserable shack where you were taking shelter from the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it seemed that you were about to be eaten by a youkai,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you tried to stand up against me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since that day... every time saw you, thought of you,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}this feeling, that keeps getting intense, is the feeling of affection.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I am in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that it was {\i1}you{\i0} who saved me by the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know that every evening you sneaked in and patted my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.18,0:05:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You are dear to me than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I may not have been the person you thought about,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but, right now, I want to answer to you as myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I already am all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I like you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I must return right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I, too, have things that I must do, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.31,0:06:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I will become your wife in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,promise me Tomoe,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When that time comes once again, don't evade it and say it properly, like just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let Yukiji-san hear it too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's the person who you should be telling all this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The future... when will that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'll be convinced by those fine words?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.51,0:07:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiji! What's the matter!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Time's up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...Tomoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Return me... to my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.98,0:07:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Goodbye, Tomoe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's meet again, after 500 years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then, we will always, always be together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull yourself together, Yukiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:07:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not good! If this keeps up, I'll disappear in front of Tomoe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we going, Tomoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The place where you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to return home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I don't know how to fix your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is... the feudal lord's manor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yukiji-san is here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, leave me there... so that no one sees us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must not run into her right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for bringing me here, Tomoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm alright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Go before people find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If I let go of this hand, I feel as if I won't be able to see you again for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That might be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This will probably be the last time that I meet the Tomoe of this era.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,promise one more time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that you'll definitely be my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And as proof of your promise, leave your hairpin with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If not, then I can't go on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.23,0:09:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you Tomoe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You believed in me and showed your affection.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The only thing that I can leave behind, is my precious memories of you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and fix your sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:09:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When that "time" that you say comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely come to get you, Yukiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just in a little while, I'll be able to save Tomoe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.95,0:10:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I must hurry to Mt. Ontake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, Nanami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikage-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright. With this, everything that you needed to do is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:11:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, all that's left is to see how the seeds that you've sown bud.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.15,0:11:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, Nanami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be the last time travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You must meet Kuromaro this last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want you to find the key to lift Tomoe's curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's on Mt. Ontake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The air feels different than before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder how much time has passed since then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.36,0:11:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Kuromaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.05,0:11:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a person who's about to die due to your spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's stiff.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fox youkai, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like that man wasn't able to marry that woman named Yukiji after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Yukiji-san!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman... died.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.67,0:12:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Died... Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Kuromaro!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I shall show you just a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...the events of that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I got my hands on a very good medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If you drink this, I'm sure, even your sickness will go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:12:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe and Yukiji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.79,0:13:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Live with me, forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.74,0:13:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right, this is an image of the past.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,For such a flashy person like you to come to these mountains, what wish might you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to become a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.53,0:13:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a woman I want to marry for life, after becoming a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.43,0:13:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomoe...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A youkai like you, having such feelings for a human woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.88,0:13:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't, tell me the person who can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.84,0:13:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I will have you risk your life for making a contract with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have that kind of a resolve?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.43,0:14:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can become a human, I'll even offer my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.17,0:14:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You feel this strongly for Yukiji-san, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a contract between you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall turn you into a human on the next full moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,However my condition is, that you must marry that woman for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are not able to keep the promise, that curse mark will eat away your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.33,0:14:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my wish from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall grant your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that woman's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:14:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman's name is Yukiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:59.42,overlap dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomoe, you idiot! Making a contract just like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She is to be my lifelong partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:04.14,overlap dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because you bet your life, the current you is about to die!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I shall have you offer an article that will stand as proof of the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,An article?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. A great youkai like you is about to become human.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a major contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why, it won't do if you don't offer something suitably precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.77,0:15:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then there's no other option than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My most precious woman's belonging.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She promised me on this hairpin, that when that "time" comes, she'll be my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise, I'll become your wife in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That "time" might be when I become a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Or some time much further than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Even then,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait, no matter how long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomoe! Me too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she promised, that the "time" would definitely come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I, too...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait, you stupid fox!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,When I return to the future, this time, I'll make you say that you like me!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll make you come with me to the aquarium repeatedly, ride the ferris wheel with you 5 times in a row,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and have you compliment me when I wear the *furisode.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:51.91,sign2,,0,0,0,,{\an 8}*Note: furisode: long sleeved kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll go back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:17:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll return to the future where Tomoe is waiting for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuromaro-san, please give that hairpin to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't return this hairpin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.77,0:17:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it belongs to this era.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take this with you to the future, you'll make Tomoe disappear from your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You must return to your time and search for this hairpin there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,For that, keep this place, where I am sleeping, in your mind very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.98,0:17:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I will die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiji died before Tomoe, and so the condition could not be fulfilled, neither by me nor by Tomoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuromaro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.85,0:17:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We, who couldn't fulfill the promise, must pay the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That is my contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you forge such a contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A human child wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.81,0:18:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I... wanted to be connected to someone... deeper and deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than living alone for ages,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.03,0:18:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I preferred to share my fate with the one I'm linked to and meet my end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my cherished desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Return to the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, human child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Kuromaro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The first time I met Tomoe,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.55,0:19:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was scared, since he was a youkai, a fox and I didn't know his nature.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And as a bonus, he had a bad attitude, was a flirt and had a bad mouth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it didn't take much time for me to fall for him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait, no matter how long it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've waited for me for 500 years, right Tomoe?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't make you wait for even one day now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must hurry back to the present and find the hairpin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm back. It's Mikage shrine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I've returned, Mikage-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:19:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,At last,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,just as Mikage-san said, it'll be over in a short while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.65,0:20:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I found out the way to break the curse! This will definitely save Tomoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, I'll be able to meet Tomoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you know about Tomoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.34,0:20:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me! Momozono Nanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The one you handed over the shrine to!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was Mikage shrine always this beautiful!?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could this be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Will you be able to save Tomoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me hear what you have to say, Nanami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikage-sama! All the fish folk are snoring in the guest room!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Let them continue sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan is working hard by herself! They're too carefree!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.03,0:21:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikage-sama too is too carefree!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you seriously thinking about Tomoe-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Of course! That's harsh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.39,0:21:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, you don't seem too worried, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why had you left for 20 years in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.38,0:21:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I invited Tomoe to be my familiar, I've always always worried about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.79,0:21:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe had a debt he needed to settle one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.79,0:21:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't know what to do for someone who didn't even know what a high price he would have to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.43,0:21:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I tried everything possible for me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.83,0:21:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But nothing I did worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.55,0:22:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, on a certain day 20 years ago, suddenly, the fog was lifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That made me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.80,0:22:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.82,0:22:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.08,0:22:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Nanami-chan!! Are you okay!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki, it hurts! My body hurts!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Nanami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.99,0:22:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You've found a way to break the curse, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.76,0:22:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.33,0:22:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It took a while.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.07,0:22:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, I'm coming to get you soon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.48,0:22:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait for me, okay Tomoe?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.67,0:22:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomoe!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.52,0:22:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can hear Nanami's voice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.98,0:22:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No... That's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:22:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yukiji's voice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.41,0:23:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's not possible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.57,0:23:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because she died a long time ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.18,0:23:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's so dark that I can't even see her face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.54,0:23:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My consiousness...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.73,0:23:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...is being eaten up... by the darkness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.93,0:23:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe, so you were sleeping in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.12,0:23:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for sealing you inside the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.49,0:23:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be just fine even if you come out of there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.90,0:23:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.38,0:23:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to a brighter place together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.94,0:23:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a cautious child.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.42,0:23:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-san has gone to retrieve the proof of your contract, for your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.68,0:23:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She has gone in the *Yogiriguruma, so she'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.68,0:23:55.70,sign2,,0,0,0,,{\an 8}*Note: Yogiriguruma= night fog (Yogiri) vehicle (kuruma)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.25,0:23:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nanami...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.24,0:24:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan, is this really the right mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.56,0:24:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.55,0:24:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a stormy night. Should we come back tomorrow when the weather's better?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.38,0:24:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Tomoe-kun won't die just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.53,0:24:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I remember that place!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.67,0:24:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan, leaning out that much is danger-
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.56,0:24:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha!! Nanami-chan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.49,0:24:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki! That's the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.39,0:24:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Lower the vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.05,0:24:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan...!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.89,0:24:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is she doing!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.20,0:24:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-san has gone to retrieve the proof of your contract in order to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.82,0:24:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's found, then your curse will be uplifted and you'll all be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.12,0:24:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.47,0:24:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you should come out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.84,0:24:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way she can erase this curse mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.34,0:24:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I let Yukiji die alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.63,0:25:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans are weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.90,0:25:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.06,0:25:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wish for anything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.39,0:25:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand humans, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.23,0:25:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They just have a different way of living than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.11,0:25:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiji left behind a child in the feudal lord's house, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.20,0:25:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.79,0:25:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That little, weak living creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.72,0:25:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think happened to that child?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.98,0:25:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have died like a stray.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.76,0:25:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.04,0:25:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That child grew up safely and gave birth to a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.77,0:25:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That child also grew up and handed her life to the next generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.04,0:25:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,By doing that, they linked to Nanami-san's generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.80,0:26:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-san is a descendant of Yukiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.86,0:26:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you, who lives for hundreds of years,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.53,0:26:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,for all those years, they linked their lives in that manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.76,0:26:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans aren't weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.95,0:26:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-san's existence is proof of their strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.08,0:26:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't disappear like bubbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.70,0:26:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,On the contrary, you're on the verge of disappearing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.88,0:26:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, come on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.10,0:26:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.69,0:26:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.05,0:26:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised me that you'd marry me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.44,0:27:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When that "time" comes, I'll become your wife.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.26,0:27:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I promise, Tomoe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.95,0:27:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We met again after 500 years with our memories lost.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.59,0:27:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was a completely different meeting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.37,0:27:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet, you were still able to find me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.95,0:27:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.33,0:27:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The curse marks are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.67,0:27:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are a ton of things that I couldn't tell you then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.00,0:27:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe, who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.33,0:27:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.93,0:27:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.17,0:27:54.78,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Hakanaki yume ga sameyaranu mama
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.17,0:27:54.78,English ED,,0,0,0,,In a lingering, fleeting dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.26,0:28:00.80,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Hanabirao hitotsu yakusoku ni shita
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.26,0:28:00.80,English ED,,0,0,0,,we made a promise on the petal.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.25,0:28:06.86,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Namao wo younde sugao ni furete
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.25,0:28:06.86,English ED,,0,0,0,,Calling my name, touching me earnestly,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.31,0:28:12.87,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Shiranai toshitsuki umeru te no hira
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.31,0:28:12.87,English ED,,0,0,0,,for many years, your hands held mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.36,0:28:23.50,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Midareta kami wo nanimo iwazuni naoshite kureta
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.36,0:28:23.50,English ED,,0,0,0,,Without saying a word, you fixed my disheveled hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.66,0:28:28.02,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Ne
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.66,0:28:28.02,English ED,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.62,0:28:34.83,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Sakurani kotoba toki no wakuraba
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.62,0:28:34.83,English ED,,0,0,0,,By the cherry blossoms' sacred words,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.83,0:28:40.60,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Oikaketeita anatano senaka
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.83,0:28:40.60,English ED,,0,0,0,,I'd been chasing your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.60,0:28:46.15,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Furimuita hitomi wa kagayasashikute
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.60,0:28:46.15,English ED,,0,0,0,,You turned around with gentle eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.90,0:28:52.66,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Senobi wo shitara todoku kigashita
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.90,0:28:52.66,English ED,,0,0,0,,If I tiptoed, I might reach you,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.92,0:28:58.80,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Sono kyori sae mo tada suki datta
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.92,0:28:58.80,English ED,,0,0,0,,Even from afar, my love in unwavering
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.80,0:29:04.32,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Hitogo tsunoru omoi, dakishimeta mama
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.80,0:29:04.32,English ED,,0,0,0,,My feelings get stronger every time you hug me close.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.06,0:29:13.17,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Ikutsumono haru wo someteku
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.06,0:29:13.17,English ED,,0,0,0,,You brought color to many springtimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.92,0:29:22.48,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Binetsu no hibi gaa susaburu kaze ga
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.92,0:29:22.48,English ED,,0,0,0,,The mildly feverish days, the rough winds,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.00,0:29:28.54,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Hanabira wo tsuyoku irozukete ita
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.00,0:29:28.54,English ED,,0,0,0,,were strongly coloring the petals.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.04,0:29:34.60,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Isakai wo shite mata yorisotte
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.04,0:29:34.60,English ED,,0,0,0,,We fought then cuddled close to each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.07,0:29:40.66,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Dochiraga tomonaku tsunagu te no hida
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.07,0:29:40.66,English ED,,0,0,0,,Somewhere along the line our hands got linked together.
