Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.63,0:29:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just how much I love you,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.69,0:29:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}from now on, I'm going to tell you that many times.{\i0}